snippet.title: Jhaliko ‡§ù‡§≤‡§ø‡§ï‡•ã - Arjun Sapkota | Melina Rai | Samikshya Adhikari | Kusum Bhandari | New Nepali Song
snippet.description:
This is the story of a young Nepali youth who leaves his home, family, and village to chase small dreams in a foreign land. But will those dreams come true? Or will fate write a different ending? A journey filled with hope, struggle, and silence and a truth that reveals itself only at the end. Watch till the last moment. some stories don‚Äôt end, they stay in your heart forever.

Arjun Sapkota Presents: New Nepali Song 2082

snippet.description:
Immerse yourself in the enchanting melodies of Alka Yagnik, a voice that defined romance in the 2000s. This collection features the timeless gem "Ikrar Ho Na Jaye" from the movie Zinda Dil, a song that captures the tender emotions of love and longing. Alka Yagnik's voice is a vessel of heartfelt expressions, her renditions painting vivid tapestries of affection and passion. Her songs transport us to a world where love reigns supreme, and every note resonates with the purest emotions. 

Experience the magic of these unforgettable songs, each a testament to Alka Yagnik's unparalleled artistry. Let the music evoke cherished memories and stir the depths of your heart. Indulge in the sweet nostalgia of the 2000s and revel in the beauty of these timeless compositions.



Credits :

Song: Ikrar Ho Na Jaye
Album: Zinda Dil
Artist: Alka Yagnik
Music Director: Nadeem-Shravan
Lyricist: Sameer

snippet.description:
Prince Narula Music presents the brand new Haryanvi song ‚ÄúBolero‚Äù.
Written by Raees & music produced by Jaymeet - a pure desi vibe and powerful energy!

#bolero #bolerosong #princenarula #komalchaudhry #pranjaldahiya #harynavisong #haryanvi

Ft - Pranjal Dahiya 
Lyrics & composer - Raees 
Music By - Jaymeet
Mix Master - Baxbee

Rajasthan‚Äôs Leading Royal Wedding Destination Resort
Filming Location - Lohagarh Fort Resort, Jaipur
Stay Partner - Lohagarh Fort Resort & Spa

üåê Website:
https://www.lohagarhfortresort.in/

üì∏ Instagram:

https://www.facebook.com/lohagarhfortresort

‚ñ∂Ô∏è YouTube Channel:
https://youtube.com/@LohagarhFortResortAndSpa?si=FdkmHXo0YqyenszN

üì© Email: bookings@lohagarhfortresort.com

Streaming Links: 
‚ô™ Insta Reels: https://www.instagram.com/reels/audio/1295898955639597?igsh=MWRkcXF3cGZ3dWUyeQ==

‚ô™ Amazon Music: https://music.amazon.com/tracks/B0G271BZG1

‚ô™ Apple Music: https://music.apple.com/us/album/bolero-feat-pranjal-dahiya/1852860832?i=1852861073&app=music

‚ô™ Jio Saavn: https://www.jiosaavn.com/song/bolero-feat.-pranjal-dahiya/AAldeB11ZVI

‚ô™ YouTube Music: https://music.youtube.com/watch?v=5jGVUGF6vxg

Lyrics:
Manne Thar se pasand lakha‚Äôan baar keh li
Mere saiyaan ji ne phir te bolero le li 
Oo Manne Thar se pasand lakha‚Äôan baar keh li
Mere saiyaan ji ne phir te bolero le li 

Akhan utte Cartier dabb ch clip hai 
Utte kali raat ae te chle chitti whip hai 
Veri saare RIP ae ni munda aaya game ch ni 
Russian weapon ae ni kithe equip hai 

Banda cloud billo sadde maare fire da 
Munda billo vajda shikari tere sheher da 
Mere ala bhreya ae heere jeha yaar ni
Banake de du koka billo tere nakk size da 

Kyu rakhe se dil maila kyu gaadi na maili 
Mere saiyaan ji ne phir te Bolero le li
Manne Thar se pasand lakha‚Äôan baar keh li
Mere saiyaan ji ne phir te bolero le li 

Tu kaafile mein aave teri khabar aave akhbaara mein 
Gaadi ke bheettar haande se yaara gail tu daara mein 
Raees mein tujhse rooth gayi naa likh ke manne manaave tu 
Gail raakhe weapon mein dabban ke paas na aave tu

Tyre jaave fookdi ni car jaave shookdi 
Ronda di fragrance maarda sandook ni
Mucchan saddi khadiyan akhan saddi chadhiyan 
Gutt naal laggiyan ne mehngi mehngi ghadiyan
Bhann dinde adiyan te bhann de groor billo
Maal peya khidyaa te chehre utte noor billo
Saare din bhajje rehnde yaariyan de kamm nu
Ni sadde kolo‚Äôn rehndiyan ne aalsan vi door billo

Meri rail banaake tu yaaran gail jaave raili 
Mere saiyaan ji ne phir te bolero le li 
Oh Manne Thar se pasand lakha‚Äôan baar keh li
Mere saiyaan ji ne phir te bolero le li 

Subh billboard mein re shaam ne vivaadan mein 
Choriyan ke dilaan mein Daroga geri kaada mein 
Chora Haryane aala paisa bole khaata‚Äôan mein
Bole mhara naam chori bolun koni jaada main 
Bhaichaara sath mere laath le re haath mein 
Vairi agge sheher mere raat chore kaat re
Engine V8 ka yo maare dekh laat re 
Dekh tu vajan chori kalli kalli baat mein

Chore hove charche mein chore hove parche mein 
Kare na kanjoosi koi chore kadde kharche mien 
Choreyaan ka naam bole choreyaan ka kaam bole
Hello hii bolte na chore Raam Raam bole 

Faridabad se Chandigarh tk baat faili 
Mere Saiyaan ji ne phir te Bolero le li
Oh Manne Thar se pasand lakha‚Äôan baar keh li
Mere saiyaan ji ne phir te bolero le li 

Tola hathan ch te jeb ch staang ni
Ta baajan to vi ucchiyan udaariyan
Pataa lagg janda billo Chandigarh nu
Te assi Phirni to mod li Faraari‚Äôyaan

Naara‚Äôan jach ke aundiyan jattan vaaste 
Sampark banaun na aa firdi 
Jide picche ae ni bombay saara kamla 
Fan mittran di hoii bade chir di

Lagge pent house vich kude mehfilan
Nede baddlan de khulle Balvenie ni 
Ajj oh hi billo naal sadde behnde aa 
School behnde si jo naal canteen ni

Itvaar pive whisky hukka chaale daily
Mere saiyaan ji ne phir te Bolero le li 
Oh Manne Thar se pasand lakha‚Äôan baar keh li
Mere saiyaan ji ne phir te bolero le li
